The Government Medical College, Akola, an institution under the Department of Ear, Nose and Throat Services, is being granted administrative sanction for the purchase of machinery and equipment mentioned in the blank table on a turnkey basis from the funds sanctioned under the State Plan for the financial year 2024-25 -Rs 7,56,00, 000 / - (Rupees Seven Crores, Fifty Six Lakhs only) (inclusive of all taxes), subject to the following conditions:
Conditions: - 1) This administrative approval 2024-25 is being made in this financial year from the funds sanctioned and available under the State Plan to the institution concerned.
